description:
Elizabeth Thorn steps in today to fill the 10th spot that was left vacant after Rain Degrey announced she had a rib injury. We could either forfeit Rain's match altogether and let Penny walk right on to the next round in the Summer Vengeance Tournament, or we could find a girl who was willing to take a match on short to notice. Elizabeth stepped up. Elizabeth has big shoes to fill but she is a student black belt in a few different martial arts and she shows promise. Elizabeth isn't well versed in the way of the Ultimate Surrender and she hasn't trained in nearly a decade. She lost her first match against Yasmin loven. Penny is pretty sure she will mop the floor with Elizabeth the same way that she mopped the floor with Yasmin during the Welter Weight Tournament.
Winner utterly humiliates the losers. Spits in her Face, Squirts on her then Shaves her pussy hair and glues it to her face with Honey. Loser left Genuinely humiliated
title: Summer Vengeance wrestlers ranked 10th and 9th meet on the mats
